thread.title: BRIEF-India's Canara Bank Dec Qtr Profit Falls About 61 Pct

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-India's Canara Bank Dec Qtr Profit Falls About 61 Pct

organizations.name: canara bank dec qtr profit falls about

text:
Jan 24 (Reuters) - Canara Bank Ltd:
* DEC QUARTER NET PROFIT 1.26 BILLION RUPEES VERSUS PROFIT OF 3.22 BILLION RUPEES YEAR AGO
* CONSENSUS FORECAST FOR DEC QUARTER NET PROFIT WAS 2 BILLION RUPEES
* DEC QUARTER INTEREST EARNED 107.75 BILLION RUPEES VERSUS 102.88 BILLION RUPEES YEAR AGO
* DEC QUARTER PROVISIONS AND CONTIGENCIES 26.74 BILLION RUPEES VERSUS 14.85 BILLION RUPEES YEAR AGO
* DEC QUARTER PROVISIONS FOR NON-PERFORMING ASSETS 19 BILLION RUPEES VERSUS 14.87 BILLION RUPEES YEAR AGO
* DEC QUARTER GROSS NPA 10.38 PERCENT VERSUS 10.51 PERCENT PREVIOUS QUARTER
* DEC QUARTER NET NPA 6.78 PERCENT VERSUS 7.02 PERCENT PREVIOUS QUARTER Source text: bit.ly/2F8lSlS Further company coverage:
